MultiFileRAG System
The MultiFileRAG System is a specialized implementation of LightRAG for processing PDF, CSV, and image files, providing enhanced data analysis, visualization, and querying capabilities powered by local LLMs through Ollama.

Local LLM Integration
Local LLM Integration uses Ollama to run models locally without relying on external APIs, a key feature of the MultiFileRAG System.

PDF Processing
